   <title>First Post</title>
   <link href="https://cyb3rdan.com/2018/11/16/First-Post/"/>
   <updated>2018-11-16T00:00:00+10:30</updated>
   <id>https://cyb3rdan.com/2018/11/16/First-Post</id>
   <content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Creating a blog is something I’ve been wanting to do for a while now, but there have been so many more important things going on in my life that meant I just never got around to it.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;In terms of content, I have been focusing quite a lot on &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.hackthebox.eu/&quot;&gt;Hack The Box&lt;/a&gt; lately, and I will likely start with some walkthroughs once I get around to making my notes more complete.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;!--more--&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Other than walkthroughs, I will be starting my &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.offensive-security.com/information-security-certifications/oscp-offensive-security-certified-professional/&quot;&gt;OSCP&lt;/a&gt; journey soon, and am planning to add my thoughts to the many others who have been through the same process before me. The hope is that if I can write about certain tools and processes that it will only increase my chances of passing on my first attempt.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;If that sort of stuff is of any interest to you, then keep an eye out for more posts.&lt;/p&gt;
</content>
